title: Who is the Best in the AFC?
itunes:title: Who is the Best in the AFC?
description:
The Good Morning Football Crew decide who is the best in the AFC. The gang also discusses what we learned from week 6. Lastly, Kay Adams, Nate Burleson, Peter Schrager, and Kyle Brandt give you their underappreciated storylines. Be sure to check in every Wednesday to the GMFB podcast! Like, share, subscribe!
